name: chi2comb-py
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "chi2comb-py" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/chi2comb/chi2comb-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e1605e065747a04c95a244ac4dd727af06a0f99a22f3d4ff549b2ebdcafee7aa

build:
  number: 4
  skip: true  # [py27 or python_impl == 'pypy']
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - cffi >=1.11.5
    - chi2comb >=0.0.3
    - pip
    - pytest-runner >=5
    - python
    - setuptools >=49.6.0
  run:
    - pytest-doctestplus >=0.8.0
    - cffi >=1.11.5
    - chi2comb >=0.0.3
    - pytest >=5
    - pytest-runner >=5
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - chi2comb

about:
  home: https://github.com/limix/chi2comb-py
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.md
  summary: Linear combination of independent noncentral chi-squared random variables
  dev_url: https://github.com/limix/chi2comb-py

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Horta
